ability.description:
@Passive.type@: Attacks deal @BonusMagicDamage.values@ (@BonusMagicDamage.scaling@) @BonusMagicDamage.type@.
After every @ThirdAttack.values@ @ThirdAttack.type@, throw @CardsCount.values@ @CardsCount.type@ in a @Cone.type@ that deal @CardsDamage.values@ (@CardsDamage.scaling@) @CardsDamage.type@, reduced by @DamageReduction.values@ for each @Enemy.type@ they pass through.

@PartnersInCrime.type@: When you field Graves and Twisted Fate, both gain bonuses.

@Passive.type@: Attacks @Ricochet.type@ to the @HighestHealthEnemy.values@ @HighestHealthEnemy.type@, dealing @RicochetDamage.values@ @RicochetDamage.type@.

@Active.type@: Fire waves of @Bullets.type@ that land on the @NearestEnemies.values@ @NearestEnemies.type@. The first wave deals @FirstWaveDamage.values@ (@FirstWaveDamage.scaling@) @FirstWaveDamage.type@ and the rest deal @SecondaryWaveDamage.values@ (@SecondaryWaveDamage.scaling@) @SecondaryWaveDamage.type@.
Every @ThirdCast.values@ @ThirdCast.type@, increase the number of waves by @WaveIncrease.values@.

@Passive.type@: @Takedowns.values@ @Takedowns.type@ grant permanent @MaxHealth.type@.

@Active.type@: Gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
When it breaks, deal @ExplosionDamage.values@ (@ExplosionDamage.scaling@) @ExplosionDamage.type@ to @AdjacentEnemies@.

@Passive.type@: If Draven has an @EmpoweredAxe.type@ in hand, his next attack will throw it.
On @Takedown.type@, gain an @AdorationStack.type@, doubled if Draven or Darius scored the kill.
Every @AdorationStacksThreshold.values@ @AdorationStacksThreshold.type@ grants @Gold.values@ @Gold.type@.

@Active.type@: Spin an @EmpoweredAxe.type@ that replaces his basic attack and deals @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ and returns to Draven after hitting an @Enemy.type@.

@Passive.type@: Damaging an @Enemy.type@ applies @ShredPercent.values@ @Shred.type@ for @ShredDuration.values@ @ShredDuration.type@.
@Active.type@: Kick @Bubbles.values@ bubbles at @NearbyEnemies.values@ @NearbyEnemies.type@, dealing @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@ and @ChillPercent.values@ @Chilled.type@ for @ChillDuration.values@ @ChillDuration.type@.

@Shred.type@: Reduce @MagicResist.type@

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

@Passive.type@: Reduce instances of incoming damage by @DamageReduction.values@ (@DamageReduction.scaling@).

@Active.type@: Call down @SunBeams.type@ on the @NearestEnemies.values@ @NearestEnemies.type@, @Stunned.type@ them for @StunDuration.values@ @StunDuration.type@ and dealing @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@.
@Wound.type@ and @BurnPercent.values@ @BurnPercent.type@ them for @BurnDuration.values@ @BurnDuration.type@.

@Wound.type@: Reduce Healing Received by 33%.

@Burn.type@: Deal a percent of the target's Max Health as True Damage every second.

Start with @Infernum.type@ equipped.
On cast, switch to @Severum.type@ for @SeverumAttacks.values@ @SeverumAttacks.type@.

@Infernum.type@: Attacks hit @EnemiesHit.values@ @EnemiesHit.type@ and apply @Sunder.values@ @Sunder.type@ for @SunderDuration.values@ @SunderDuration.type@.

@Severum.type@: Gain @BonusAttackSpeed.values@ @BonusAttackSpeed.type@ and @Omnivamp.values@ @Omnivamp.type@.
Attacks are replaced with swipes that deal @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@.

@Sunder.type@: Reduce @Armor.type@

Fire an ice shard at target that deals @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@.
If they are @Chilled.type@, the damage @CriticallyStrikes.type@.

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

Fire an arrow at @Target.type@ that deals @Damage.values@ (@Damage.scaling@) @Damage.type@ to them.
Deal @AdjacentDamage.values@ (@AdjacentDamage.scaling@) @Damage.type@ to @AdjacentEnemies.type@.
Targets below @ExecuteThreshold.values@ @ExecuteThreshold.type@ take @TrueDamage.type@ instead.
@ChillPercent.values@ @ChillPercent.type@ @AllEnemies.type@ hit for @ChillDuration.values@ @ChillDuration.type@.

@BloodswornBond.type@: Attacks fire a bonus arrow for every @BonusADPercent.values@ @BonusADPercent.type@ granted to Tryndamere by Bloodsworn Bond.
These arrows deal @BonusArrowDamage.values@ (@BonusArrowDamage.scaling@) @BonusArrowDamage.type@.

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

Encase @Target.type@ in ice, @Stunned.type@ them for @StunDuration.values@ @StunDuration.type@ and dealing @PrimaryMagicDamage.values@ (@PrimaryMagicDamage.scaling@) @PrimaryMagicDamage.type@.
All @EnemiesWithin.values@ @EnemiesWithin.type@ split @SplitMagicDamage.values@ (@SplitMagicDamage.scaling@) @SplitMagicDamage.type@.
If the @Target.type@ dies, shards fly out and split excess damage between the @NearestEnemies.values@ @NearestEnemies.type@.
@ChilledEnemies.values@ @ChilledEnemies.type@ take @ChillAmp.values@ more damage from this @Ability.type@.

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

@Leap.type@ at @Target.type@ and gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
Slam down after a brief delay, dealing @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@ to @Enemies.values@ @Enemies.type@ and @ChillPercent.values@ @ChillPercent.type@ them for @ChillDuration.values@ @ChillDuration.type@.

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

Gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
@Slam.type@ on @Target.type@, dealing @PrimaryDamage.values@ (@PrimaryDamage.scaling@) @PrimaryDamage.type@ to @Enemies.type@ in a @PrimaryRange.values@ @PrimaryRange.type@.
Every @ThirdCast.values@ @ThirdCast.type@ deals @SecondaryDamage.values@ (@SecondaryDamage.scaling@) @SecondaryDamage.type@ in a @SecondaryRange.values@ @SecondaryRange.type@ instead and @KnockedUp.type@ @Enemies.type@ hit for @KnockupDuration.values@ @KnockupDuration.type@.

@Dash.type@, then deal @Damage.values@ (@Damage.scaling@) @Damage.type@ to @Adjacent.type@ @Enemies@.
If only @Enemy.values@ @Enemy.type@ is hit, deal @DoubleDamage.type@.

@BladeBrothers.type@: When Yone casts, your strongest Yasuo @Blinks.type@ to every @Target.type@ Yone hits and deals @BladeBrothersDamage.values@ @BladeBrothersDamage.type@ to each.

@Erupt.type@ the @Battlefield.type@ in @Flames.type@, permanently @Burning.type@ and @Wounding.type@ all @Enemies.type@ and dealing @BurnDamage.values@ (@BurnDamage.scaling@) @BurnDamage.type@ to each of them over @BurnDuration.values@ @BurnDuration.type@.

Annie's max @Mana.type@ is @Reduced.type@ by @ManaReduction.values@ for the rest of combat. @SubsequentCasts.type@ launch a @Fireball.type@ at a @Target.type@ that deals @FireballDamage.values@ (@FireballDamage.scaling@) @FireballDamage.type@.

@Burn.type@: Deal a percent of the @Target.type@'s max @Health.type@ as @TrueDamage.type@ every @Second.type@.
@Wound.type@: Reduce @Healing.type@ received by @WoundPercent.values@.

@Summon.type@ an @Elemental.type@ from behind the @FarthestEnemy.values@ @FarthestEnemy.type@.
It @ChillPercent.values@ @ChillPercent.type@ @EnemiesHit.type@ for @ChillDuration.values@ @ChillDuration.type@ and deals @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@ to them.

When it arrives, @Headbutt.type@ it and @Redirect.type@ it toward @AnotherEnemy.values@ @AnotherEnemy.type@, dealing @RedirectDamage.values@ (@RedirectDamage.scaling@) @RedirectDamage.type@ instead.

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

@Passive.type@: After @Witnessing.type@ @AttackCount.values@ @AttackCount.type@ from @Azir.type@, @SandSoldiers.type@ deal @PassiveDamage.values@ (@PassiveDamage.scaling@) @PassiveDamage.type@ to their @Target.type@.

@Active.type@: @Summon.type@ a @SandSoldier.type@ near @Target.type@ and @Command.type@ them to @Strike.type@.
If @SoldierCount.values@ @SoldierCount.type@ are already out, they all immediately deal @ActiveDamage.values@ (@ActiveDamage.scaling@) @ActiveDamage.type@ instead.

@Teleport.type@ into the @LargestCluster.values@ @LargestCluster.type@ and @Stun.type@ them for @StunDuration.values@ @StunDuration.type@.
@BeginCasting.type@, losing @ManaDrain.values@ @ManaDrain.type@.
While casting, deal @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@ per @Interval.values@ @Interval.type@ to @AllEnemies.type@ within a @Radius.values@ @Radius.type@.
The @ClosestEnemies.values@ @ClosestEnemies.type@ take @BonusDamage.values@ more damage.

@DragonsDescent.type@: @Transform.type@ into a @Dragon.type@, gaining @MaxHealth.values@ @MaxHealth.type@.
Briefly gain @Durability.values@ @Durability.type@ and @DiveBomb.type@ into the @LargestGroup.values@ @LargestGroup.type@, dealing @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ in a @Circle.values@ @Circle.type@.

@FlameBreath.type@: @Breath.type@ fire in a @Cone.type@ for @Duration.values@ @Duration.type@, dealing @BreathDamage.values@ (@BreathDamage.scaling@) @BreathDamage.type@ each @Interval.values@ @Interval.type@ to @EnemiesHit.type@.

@Passive.type@: Every @AttackInterval.values@ @AttackInterval.type@ deals @PassiveDamage.values@ (@PassiveDamage.scaling@) @PassiveDamage.type@ in a @Circle.type@ around the @Target.type@.

@Active.type@: @Dash.type@ into the @LargestGroup.values@ @LargestGroup.type@ and @Inspire.type@ @AllAllies.type@ within @AlliesRange.values@ @AlliesRange.type@, granting them @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
Then @CrashDown.type@, dealing @ActiveDamage.values@ (@ActiveDamage.scaling@) @ActiveDamage.type@ to @AllEnemies.type@ within @EnemiesRange.values@ @EnemiesRange.type@.

@Passive.type@: @Immune.type@ to @CrowdControl.type@.
Attacks briefly @KnockUp.type@ the @Target.type@ and deal @PassiveDamage.values@ @PassiveDamage.type@ in a @PassiveRadius.values@ @PassiveRadius.type@ around them.

@Active.type@: @Slam.type@ the @Ground.type@, dealing @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ to @AllEnemies.type@, reduced by @DamageReduction.values@ for each @Hex.type@ from the @Center.type@ (@MinDamage.values@).
If this is the @FirstTime.type@ they've been hit by @SeismicSlam.type@ this @Combat.type@, @KnockThemUp.type@ for @KnockUpDuration.values@ @KnockUpDuration.type@.
@Summon.type@ @RockCount.values@ @RockCount.type@ that fall around the @Battlefield.type@, each dealing @RockDamage.values@ (@RockDamage.scaling@) @RockDamage.type@ to @EnemiesHit.type@.

@Passive.type@: Attacks fire a @Barrage.type@ of @BulletCount.values@ @BulletCount.type@.

@Active.type@: Gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ and begin consuming @ManaPerSecond.values@ @ManaPerSecond.type@.
Each @Interval.values@ @Interval.type@ while active, fire a @Laser.type@ that deals @LaserDamage.values@ (@LaserDamage.scaling@) @LaserDamage.type@, reduced by @DamageReduction.values@ per @Enemy.type@ hit up to @MaxReduction.values@.
Additionally, launch @MissileCount.values@ (@MissileCount.scaling@) @MissileCount.type@ split between @NearbyEnemies.values@ @NearbyEnemies.type@ that each deal @MissileDamage.values@ (@MissileDamage.scaling@) @MissileDamage.type@.

@Passive.type@: On @Takedown.type@, gain @AttackSpeed.values@ stacking @AttackSpeed.type@ that decays over @DecayDuration.values@ @DecayDuration.type@.

@Active.type@: Deal @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@ in a @Radius.values@ @Radius.type@ and transform for the rest of @Combat.type@.
While transformed, gain @TransformedAS.values@ @AttackSpeed.type@, @MaxHealthBonus.values@ Max Health, and increased @MoveSpeed.type@.
Attacks deal @TrueDamage.values@ @TrueDamage.type@, increased by @HitIncrease.values@ for each time the same @Enemy.type@ is hit.

@Passive.type@: After dealing @AbilityDamage.type@ to an @Enemy.type@, gain @Stardust.type@.
@Stardust.type@ makes @TheSkiesDescend.type@ more powerful.

@Active.type@: @Crash.type@ a @Star.type@ on @Target.type@, dealing @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@ in a @Radius.values@ @Radius.type@.

@StardustUpgrades.type@:
@Upgrade15.values@: Create a @Shockwave.type@ that deals @ShockwaveDamage.values@ (@ShockwaveDamage.scaling@) @ShockwaveDamage.type@ in a @ShockwaveRadius15.values@ @ShockwaveRadius15.type@.
@Upgrade60.values@: The @StarCrash.type@ deals @BonusDamage60.values@ more damage.
@Upgrade100.values@: @Shockwave.type@ increases to a @ShockwaveRadius100.values@ @ShockwaveRadius100.type@.
@Upgrade175.values@: @KnockUp.type@ @Targets.type@ in the @StarCrash.type@ for @KnockUpDuration.values@ @KnockUpDuration.type@.
@Upgrade250.values@: @Shockwave.type@ increases to @ShockwaveRadius250.values@ @ShockwaveRadius250.type@.
@Upgrade400.values@: The @StarCrash.type@ deals @BonusDamage400.values@ @BonusDamage400.type@.
@Upgrade700.values@: Also call down a @MeteorStorm.type@ that deals @MeteorDamage.values@ (@MeteorDamage.scaling@) @MeteorDamage.type@ split between @LivingEnemies.type@.
@Upgrade1400.values@: @Summon.type@ a @BlackHole.type@ at the @Epicenter.type@, @InstantlyKilling.type@ @EnemiesWithin.type@.

@Passive.type@: @Immune.type@ to @CrowdControl.type@.
Attacks deal damage in a @Line.type@ on @Target.type@.
If @NoEnemies.type@ are in @Range.type@, @Dash.type@ to the @NextOne.type@ and @KnockUp.type@ @AdjacentEnemies.type@ on arrival.

While in the @VoidRift.type@, @Erupt.type@ a @Tentacle.type@ below a @RandomEnemy.values@ @RandomEnemy.type@ every @TentacleInterval.values@ @TentacleInterval.type@ that @KnocksUp.type@ them for @TentacleDuration.values@ @TentacleDuration.type@.

@Active.type@: @Slam.type@ and @ErectSpikes.type@ in a @SpikeRadius.values@ @SpikeRadius.type@, dealing @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ to @EnemiesHit.type@.
Then over @Duration.values@ @Duration.type@, @Spit.type@ @GlobCount.values@ @GlobCount.type@ of @Acid.type@ that deal @GlobDamage.values@ (@GlobDamage.scaling@) @GlobDamage.type@.

@Passive.type@: Attacks alternate between dealing @PhysicalBonus.values@ (@PhysicalBonus.scaling@) @PhysicalBonus.type@ and @MagicBonus.values@ (@MagicBonus.scaling@) @MagicBonus.type@.

@Active.type@: Strike through the @MostEnemies.values@ @MostEnemies.type@ within @Range.values@ @Range.type@, @KnockingUp.type@ them for @KnockupDuration.values@ @KnockupDuration.type@ and dealing @ActivePhysDamage.values@ (@ActivePhysDamage.scaling@) @ActivePhysDamage.type@ and @ActiveMagicDamage.values@ (@ActiveMagicDamage.scaling@) @ActiveMagicDamage.type@.
Yone then splits @SplitPhysical.values@ (@SplitPhysical.scaling@) @SplitPhysical.type@ and @SplitMagic.values@ (@SplitMagic.scaling@) @SplitMagic.type@ among all @EnemiesHit.values@ @EnemiesHit.type@.

@BladeBrothers.type@: When Yone casts, your strongest Yasuo blinks to each target, dealing bonus physical damage.

On cast, cycle through one of the following abilities:

@Slash.type@ in a line, dealing @SlashPhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ to @Enemies.type@ hit and @SunderPercent.values@ @SunderPercent.type@ them for @SunderDuration.values@ @SunderDuration.type@.

@Swipe.type@ in a @Cone.type@, dealing @SwipePhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ to @Enemies.type@  hit and @Knock.type@ for @KnockupDuration.values@ @KnockupDuration.type@.

@Slam.type@ on @Target.type@, dealing @SlamPhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ in a @HexRadius.values@ @HexRadius.type@ circle.
@Target.type@ below @ExecuteThreshold.values@ @ExecuteThreshold.type@ are @Executed.type@.

@Bite.type@ the @Target.type@ and @Mark.type@ them, dealing @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@, increased by @DamageIncrease.values@ if they are @AlreadyMarked.type@.
After casting @CastCount.values@ @CastCount.type@, @Leap.type@ to a @NearbyHex.values@ @NearbyHex.type@, activating @Stormbringer.type@ and dealing @StormbringerDamage.values@ (@StormbringerDamage.scaling@) @StormbringerDamage.type@ to @EnemiesWithin.values@ @EnemiesWithin.type@.

@Stormbringer.type@: Gain @Health.values@ @Health.type@ and @AttackSpeed.values@ @AttackSpeed.type@.
Every @Interval.values@ @Interval.type@, summon a @LightningBolt.type@ on a @NearbyEnemy.values@ @NearbyEnemy.type@, dealing @MagicDamage.values@ (@MagicDamage.scaling@) @MagicDamage.type@.
@Takedowns.type@ summon a @Bolt.type@ on @FallenEnemies.values@ @FallenEnemies.type@.

For the next @AttackCount.values@ @AttackCount.type@, gain @Range.values@ @Range.type@ and replace attacks with a Cannon Shot.
@CannonShot.type@: deal @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@.
The @FourthShot.values@ @FourthShot.type@ deals @FourthShotMultiplier.values@ more damage.

Cast one of @SpellCount.values@ @SpellCount.type@:

@Cataclysm.type@: @Leap.type@ on a @NearbyEnemy.values@ @NearbyEnemy.type@.
Deal @CataclysmDamage.values@ (@CataclysmDamage.scaling@) @CataclysmDamage.type@ to @AllEnemies.type@ within @CataclysmRadius.values@ @CataclysmRadius.type@ and @Stun.type@ them for @StunDuration.values@ @StunDuration.type@.

@DemacianJustice.type@: Deal @JusticeDamage.values@ (@JusticeDamage.scaling@) @JusticeDamage.type@ to @Target.type@.
If they are below @ExecuteThreshold.values@ @ExecuteThreshold.type@, @Execute.type@ them.

@FinalSpark.type@: Gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
Deal @SparkDamage.values@ (@SparkDamage.scaling@) @SparkDamage.type@ to @AllEnemies.type@ in a @Line.type@.

@Release.type@ a @RunicBlast.type@, dealing @BlastDamage.values@ (@BlastDamage.scaling@) @BlastDamage.type@. @ItSplits.type@ in @ItSplits.values@, dealing @SplitPercent.values@ of the damage to the @ClosestEnemies.type@. Each @SecondaryBlast.type@ @SplitsAdditional.type@.

@Bilgewater.type@: @Explosion.type@ on impact, dealing @BilgewaterPercent.values@ of the damage as @PhysicalDamage.type@ to @AdjacentEnemies.type@.
@Demacia.type@: @Execute.type@ @Targets.type@ below @DemaciaThreshold.values@ (@DemaciaThreshold.scaling@) @DemaciaThreshold.type@.
@Freljord.type@: @Chill.type@ @Targets.type@ for @FreljordDuration.values@ @FreljordDuration.type@ and deal @FreljordBonusDamage.values@ (@FreljordBonusDamage.scaling@) @FreljordBonusDamage.type@.
@Ionia.type@: @Blasts.type@ @SplitAdditional.type@, dealing @IoniaPercent.values@ damage.
@Ixtal.type@: @Gain.type@ a random @RegionEffect.type@ on combat start and every @IxtalInterval.values@ @IxtalInterval.type@.
@Noxus.type@: @Pierce.type@ @Targets.type@, dealing @NoxusPercent.values@ reduced damage per hit.
@Piltover.type@: Every third cast is @Overcharged.type@, dealing @PiltoverPercent.values@ more damage.
@ShadowIsles.type@: Increase @BlastDamage.type@ by @ShadowIslesBonus.values@ (@ShadowIslesBonus.scaling@).
@Shurima.type@: @Knockup.type@ @Targets.type@ for @ShurimaDuration.values@ @ShurimaDuration.type@, with a chance to dredge up @GoldTreasures.type@.
@Targon.type@: @Heal.type@ the Lowest Health Ally for @TargonPercent.values@ of the damage dealt.
@Void.type@: @Ignore.type@ @VoidArmorReduction.values@ of @Enemies.type@ @Armor.type@ and @Magic.type@ Resistance.
@Yordle.type@: @Shrink.type@ @Targets.type@, lowering their damage by @YordlePercent.values@ for @YordleDuration.values@ @YordleDuration.type@.
@Zaun.type@: @Poison.type@ @Targets.type@, dealing @ZaunDamage.values@ @ZaunDamage.type@ @ZaunTimes.values@.

Become @Enraged.type@ for @EnrageDuration.values@ @EnrageDuration.type@.
While enraged, gain @Durability.values@ (@Durability.scaling@) @Durability.type@ and attacks are replaced with a strike that deals @StrikeDamage.values@ (@StrikeDamage.scaling@) @StrikeDamage.type@.
Ignore @ArmorIgnore.values@ of @Armor.type@ against @Chilled.type@ @Enemies.type@.

@BloodswornBond.type@: Gain increased @MoveSpeed.type@.
Gain @BaseAttackDamage.values@ @BaseAttackDamage.type@, permanently increased by @StackPerKill.values@ @StackPerKill.type@ whenever Ashe or Tryndamere score a kill.

@Chill.type@: Reduce @AttackSpeed.type@

@Passive.type@: While gaining @Mana.type@, throw out @OrbCount.values@ @OrbCount.type@ that @Orbit.type@ around @Target.type@.
They deal @OrbDamage.values@ (@OrbDamage.scaling@) @OrbDamage.type@ in a @OrbRadius.values@ @OrbRadius.type@ and drain @ManaDrain.values@ @ManaDrain.type@ from @EnemiesHit.type@ each @Interval.values@ @Interval.type@.
After draining @ManaThreshold.values@ @ManaThreshold.type@, gain a @RandomRadiantItem.type@. (@ItemCounter.values@)

@Active.type@: @Detonate.type@ @Orbs.type@ on @Target.type@, causing a @ExplosionRadius.values@ @ExplosionRadius.type@ @Explosion.type@ that deals @PrimaryDamage.values@ (@PrimaryDamage.scaling@) @PrimaryDamage.type@ to @Target.type@ and @SecondaryDamage.values@ (@SecondaryDamage.scaling@) @SecondaryDamage.type@ to @AllOtherEnemies.type@.

@Passive.type@: Attacks fire in a @Cone.type@ on @Target.type@, dealing @SplashDamage.values@ @SplashDamage.type@ to other @Enemies.type@ hit.

@Active.type@: Fire an explosive shell at target, dealing @PhysicalDamage.values@ (@PhysicalDamage.scaling@) @PhysicalDamage.type@ split among @Enemies.type@ in a @Circle.values@ @Circle.type@.

@PartnersInCrime.type@: When you field Graves and Twisted Fate, both gain bonuses.

@Passive.type@: All @Allies.type@ gain @PassiveArmor.values@ @PassiveArmor.type@.

@Active.type@: Gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
Impale up to @NearbyEnemies.values@ @NearbyEnemies.type@ in a @Line.values@ @Line.type@, dealing @ImpaleDamage.values@ (@ImpaleDamage.scaling@) @ImpaleDamage.type@ and @Stunning.type@ them for @StunDuration.values@ @StunDuration.type@.

@Passive.type@: Ability damage from your strongest @Leona.type@ and strongest @Diana.type@ marks @Enemies.type@ as @Moonlit.type@, reducing their damage by @MoonlitReduction.values@.

@Active.type@: Gain @Shield.values@ (@Shield.scaling@) @Shield.type@ for @ShieldDuration.values@ @ShieldDuration.type@.
Unleash a bolt of lunar energy at the @FarthestNonMoonlitEnemy.type@ within @Range.values@ @Range.type@, dealing @BoltDamage.values@ (@BoltDamage.scaling@) @BoltDamage.type@.
Then @Dash.type@ to all @MoonlitEnemies.values@ @MoonlitEnemies.type@, dealing @SecondaryDamage.values@ (@SecondaryDamage.scaling@) @SecondaryDamage.type@.

@Dash.type@ through @EnemiesInPath.values@ @EnemiesInPath.type@, dealing @Damage.values@ (@Damage.scaling@) @Damage.type@ to all enemies in the path.
Then slash @SlashCount.values@ @SlashCount.type@, each dealing @Damage2.values@ (@Damage2.scaling@) @Damage2.type@.
Subsequent casts increase the number of slashes by @SlashIncreasePerCast.values@.

